{"tid":1417144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極權最怕咩？人民能收能放","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:56:43.000Z","uid":271554,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e24408a97453bd9321777e41a2701f5bd8b23c96","tid":1417144,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講，<br />\n極權政府其實唔特別怕你地武力抗掙<br />\n燒車炸屋扑頭打劫，<br />\n佢地樣樣預算過（當然港犬執行得好差啦）<br />\n<br />\n但往往呢啲政府最怕嘅係你班人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">收放自如</span></span></strong><br />\n亦即係所謂嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有號招力</span></span></strong><br />\n當然而家無一個領䄂人物係唔易做到，<br />\n但我地都發展咗咁多創新項目出黎，<br />\n相信呢個係一定可以應付到。<br />\n<br />\n目前不得不承認去到樽項位，有人已經習慣/麻木<br />\n而我方做啲咩林鄭同黑警都唔會退讓（除非俘虜人質或出人命⋯不，都未必）<br />\n當突破唔到時又唔去舖排下一步士氣好易自己流失<br />\n一被淡化就HIHI<br />\n<br />\n尊重前線與後勤<br />\n但請務必記住<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">能收能放</span></span></strong>，先至係最大力量"},{"pid":"4a5dd9ce08f321d30f007dbfd5c99e43238263c3","tid":1417144,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d369ea7dc502a0ef9968e24b05d0511c9031f65a","tid":1417144,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88c9cc35966395e82fbe1116917a5b2483062404","tid":1417144,"uid":222190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001531_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001531_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=7a8ce82d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001532_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.